        Suggested in Deathly Hallows by Arthur Weasley to Ron (disguised by the
        Polyjuice Potion as Reginald 'Reg' Cattermole from Magical Maintenance)
        as the best way to clear up the incessant rain in Yaxley's office at
        the Ministry.
